information?

01:12:27.951 --> 01:12:29.984
I maintain close
relationships...

01:12:29.986 --> 01:12:32.152
with dissident intelligence
sources.

01:12:32.154 --> 01:12:33.820
Is there a way we can
verify that?

01:12:33.822 --> 01:12:35.589
No.

01:12:35.591 --> 01:12:37.525
See, that's kind of a problem
for us...

01:12:37.527 --> 01:12:39.060
