you the same thing.

01:13:34.684 --> 01:13:39.656
Don't they all get their
information from you?

01:13:43.091 --> 01:13:46.093
If you were wondering why
it took so long for me...

01:13:46.095 --> 01:13:51.865
to meet with you, it's this
smug attitude.

01:13:51.867 --> 01:13:55.735
