after Saddam Hussein is gone?

01:14:24.166 --> 01:14:25.865
All right, come on, Landay.

01:14:25.867 --> 01:14:27.701
No, no, no, he says the world
will be better off...

01:14:27.703 --> 01:14:29.203
but he doesn't say how.

01:14:29.205 --> 01:14:31.705
How would the removal
of Saddam Hussein...

01:14:31.707 --> 01:14:34.741
not plunge Iraq into a bloody
civil war?

01:14:34.743 --> 01:14:36.677
Tell us something that makes
sense...

01:14:36.679 --> 01:14:41.915
anything that makes sense, and
we'll write that story today.

01:14:41.917 --> 01:14:43.183
